collectionMetadata.name: Percentage of Normal (Academic) Level Students Who Passed Mother Tongue Language
collectionMetadata.description:
Percentage of N(A)-Level Students Who Passed Mother Tongue Language
Notes: 1)  Figures exclude N(A) students on the Through-train Programme who progress to Secondary 5 N(A) without taking the N(A)-Level Examination.
2)  Students who offer the subject at a higher level are also taken into consideration.

datasetMetadata.name: Percentage of N(A)-Level Students with Grade C5 or better in Mother Tongue Language
datasetMetadata.description:
(1) Figures exclude N(A) students on the Through-train Programme who progress to Secondary 5 N(A) without taking the N(A)-Level Examination.		

(2) Students who offer the subject at a more demanding level are also taken into consideration.
